    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Tremaster mirabilis. USNM E46295 A. USNM E46295 Abactinal surface. B. USNM E46295, Abactinal surfacelateral view. C. USNM E46295, Closeup of actinal surface. D. USNM 1116295, view of disk dissected, surface removed showing interradial chambers. E. Tremaster mirabilis, X-ray of MNHN IE-2006-806 (Kerguelen Island). F. Tremaster mirabilis, USNM E37444, Cutaway view of near-oral surface showing interradial chambers which open to openings on interradial actinal surface." ;
